{
  "texts": [
    "This two-year period aimed to capture publications evaluating LLM healthcare applications since the public launch of ChatGPT in November 2022.",
    "Given our hypothesis that the current landscape lacks the necessary elements needed to truly assess LLM performance in healthcare, we included a broad spectrum of studies.",
    "Citations were imported into EndNote 21 (Clarivate) for analysis.",
    "Each study was categorized by evaluation data type, healthcare task, NLP/NLU task, dimension of evaluation, and medical specialty.",
    "Healthcare task categories were developed using publicly available healthcare task and competency lists and were refined by consulting board-certified MDs 16 17 as outlined in Table 1."
  ]
}